# Cloudflare Pages: browser-cache the Plotly bundle. This applies when Pages
# serves directly on *.pages.dev (production origin + PR previews); the Worker
# sets the same header on the emroch.com/r2-dashboard path. Fixed filename + a
# day of caching (cheap ETag revalidation after) — no version churn, and a
# stale copy after a rare plotly bump still renders (stable API) and self-heals.
/plotly.min.js
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
